snippet.title: Demonetisation: Petrol Pumps Not to Accept old Notes of Rs 500 Anymore

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Petrol pumps will not to accept old currency notes of Rs 500 anymore. Peoples rushed to the petrol pumps to get petrol or diesel from old notes before mid-night.
